criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy elite swimmers engaged in competitive training for a minimum period of three
             years;

          -  Individuals with no disability;

          -  Individuals aged between 14 and 40 years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Individuals presenting co-morbidities or physical impairment that affects regular
             training;

          -  Smokers;

          -  Athletes already in a regular respiratory muscle training program

          -  Individuals with a predicted forced expiratory volume in the first second (FEV1) below
             60%.
